Package: kmOptimizer
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Survival Cutpoints
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Piotr Tymoszuk <piotr.tymoszuk@gmail.com>
Description: Finds the optimal variable cutoff stratifying the observations 
    into high and low survival subsets. The cutoff is determined based on the 
    maximal difference in survival determined by Kaplan-Meier method.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
